"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"チュチュ","body":"だからこそ、これからもワタシたちは\nワタシたちのやりたいようにやるだけ。\n誰かの思い通りになんて絶対にならない","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"ev237-me1-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"チュチュ","body":"ワタシを子供だと侮った音楽業界、世界のすべてを\n変えてみせる。このワタシが……いえ、RASが変えてみせる。\n今に見ているがいいわ……！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"ev237-me1-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"まりな","body":"ふふ、そっか。いろいろあったみたいだけど、\nチュチュちゃんもみんなもその意気なら、大丈夫そうだね","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev237-me1-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"まりな","body":"あっ、そうか。\nだからなのかな……？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"surprised01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev237-me1-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySo